# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your key. ".env" is git-ignored.
# Get a Google Gemini API key at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#
# Used by:
#   - live mode (the realtime native-audio model)
#   - the "gemini" local TTS engine (optional)
# Local mode (faster-whisper + Ollama + MeloTTS) needs NO key.
#
# The key value is never printed or logged. Never commit your real key.
GEMINI_API_KEY=
